	   <tr><td colspan=2>if your target is stationary run out to the edge of max range of you bolt spell and cast.&nbsp;&nbsp;recast right after the first one and you will hit the mob twice before it closes to melee range.  take it from there.  very simple but overlooked tactic.  softens up the mob good before the fight really starts.  example, i am level 39.  i hit twice for 330.  660 damage before the melee starts isn't a bad handicap for the fight.<br>mathus darkmage - the rathe<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
