	   <tr><td colspan=2>you will use nothing BUT bolts when you start soloing Hill Giants. The Beauty of the bolt spells is that you can successfully nuke the @#%^ out of something and still stay OUT of the Aggro range of the mob. Meaning, if you stand at the limit range of your bolt, while your earth pet has that hill giant rooted, all you do is fire bolt after bolt. Shocks wont work because of the shorter range. Youll see those hill giants go down fast and you will be VERY thankful that you have bolts. :) <br><br><br>Nahualli<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
